25
00:02:08,161 --> 00:02:09,897
Even so,

26
00:02:11,164 --> 00:02:15,435
one should fully embrace that as well.

27
00:02:16,170 --> 00:02:17,971
A man's love is...

28
00:02:18,672 --> 00:02:21,408
the endless sea.

29
