(Episode 6, Passionate Goodbye)

30
00:02:27,114 --> 00:02:28,849
This is outrageous.

31
00:02:29,383 --> 00:02:31,752
You're saying everything's over
without any notice.

32
00:02:31,752 --> 00:02:32,986
Do you think a contract is a joke?

33
00:02:32,986 --> 00:02:34,254
